      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i just cut my forearm pretty bad while cooking and its still kinda oozing blood even after i put pressure on it for a bit. it looks pretty deep. im in cape town and dont really want to deal with the hospital wait times if i can avoid it... do u think i can just clean it out and put some honey on it and bandage it up? i heard honey is really good for healing wounds naturally.",
